reviewText: Movie I got is wrong DVD code for USA.  But I could play it on my computer
UK coding. will not work in US bluray players. I wasn't aware there was a difference. really annoying to find out when its a birthday gift.

Wasn't aware of the international code differences, should have been alerted by the seller.  This won't play in either of my decks, which renders it useless to me and a waste of money.  Unless Amazon can straighten this out.
